{"tid":2130652,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警飯堂張相公開左, 張建宗竟修例政府飯堂可以開放堂食","createTime":"2020-07-29T10:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T02:38:23.000Z","uid":19552,"like":290,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"d426bd7e3fd1dc4d91e3ddf129c17429d336d9ef","tid":2130652,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"張建宗今晚係咪又要去同林大總統認錯<br />\n<br />\n政府勒令全港食肆今日（29日）起禁止堂食7日，政務司長張建宗周一（27日）呼籲公眾返辦公室用膳，政總食堂亦跟隨規定只限外賣，不准堂食。但規例實施不足一天，行政署今日向在政總工作的員工發電郵，通知由明日（30日）起，政總食堂可供堂食，但每枱只限一人，每枱相隔1.5米，並要求入內前要量體溫，非進食期間須戴口罩。"},{"pid":"2cbf300c250a1aafcdb30704bcb5263bc2cd76cc","tid":2130652,"uid":199893,"like":111,"dislike":0,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"政府部門全部例外 叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630738c10e7e02c1517d17a7f649a899b5ccf373","tid":2130652,"uid":5649,"like":130,"dislike":0,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"政府飯堂就得<br />\n公眾飯堂就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420c40a4ba112a4d25d5cf449366c568f83b453c","tid":2130652,"uid":19552,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"630738c10e7e02c1517d17a7f649a899b5ccf373","tid":2130652,"uid":5649,"like":130,"dislike":0,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"政府飯堂就得<br />\n公眾飯堂就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"為左保竣班黑警 樣樣衰衰都要做一次"},{"pid":"4b3c265131e7734242ea00bac7a9c999fa7c3de6","tid":2130652,"uid":37869,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"市民就要放棄自己的食飯權<br />\n港共就唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52612c3a86391e5dd438ce5e13146f5b58082744","tid":2130652,"uid":300420,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:39:4